#: ../../language/error_codes/E0075.md:1
msgid "E0075"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0075.md:3
msgid "Warning name: `unnecessary_view_op`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0075.md:5
msgid "Unnecessary `[:]` view operation."
msgstr "不必要的 `[:]` 视图操作。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0075.md:7
msgid ""
"When the expected type is already a view type, MoonBit can insert the "
"view conversion automatically. Writing `[:]` explicitly in that context "
"is redundant."
msgstr ""
"当期望类型已经是视图类型时，MoonBit 可以自动插入视图转换。"
"在这种上下文中显式写出 `[:]` 是冗余的。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0075.md:10
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0075.md:12
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"fn length(view : ArrayView[Int]) -> Int {\n"
"  view.length()\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  inspect(length([1, 2, 3][:]), content=\"3\")\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0075.md:16
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0075.md:18
msgid "Remove the redundant `[:]`."
msgstr "移除冗余的 `[:]`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0075.md:20
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"fn length(view : ArrayView[Int]) -> Int {\n"
"  view.length()\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  inspect(length([1, 2, 3]), content=\"3\")\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
